  "title": "Presales Technical Consultant - Cybersecurity",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a leading telecom client to hire a Cybersecurity Pre-Sales / Solution Architect to support sales teams in building strong pipelines through a consultative, solution-led approach.<br /><br />Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Partner with sales and account teams to drive new business and expand existing accounts</li><li>Translate customer needs into end-to-end security solutions</li><li>Design and present technical solutions, including architecture, proposals and proof-of-concepts</li><li>Support bid processes and pricing discussions with technical input</li><li>Work with cross-functional teams to ensure solution feasibility and delivery readiness</li><li>Stay updated on market trends, technologies and competitive landscape</li><li>Run enablement sessions and briefings for clients and internal teams</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>5-10 years of experience in cybersecurity or related technology role</li><li>Relevant security certifications are a plus</li><li>Strong understanding of security architecture across areas like IAM/PAM, endpoint, data protection, threat prevention, SASE, SIEM, DLP etc.</li><li>Good knowledge of security operations, incident response and threat management is an advantage</li><li>Familiar with data protection and security compliance standards in the region</li><li>Strong communication and stakeholder management skills</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced, dynamic environment</li></ul>",
